<i>Jay Park, Let's go</i>

187
00:09:11,739 --> 00:09:12,770
(Kian84's world-class lineup)

188
00:09:12,770 --> 00:09:14,509
(Kian84's work lineup)

189
00:09:14,710 --> 00:09:17,679
- Spiderman. Batman. Superman.
- I see.

190
00:09:19,139 --> 00:09:20,679
- "Fashion King."
<i>- Let's go</i>

191
00:09:22,579 --> 00:09:25,980
(They head deeper into the mountain
while Kian84 shows off his works.)

192
00:09:26,679 --> 00:09:28,389
This place is impressive.

193
00:09:32,360 --> 00:09:34,160
The roads are very rough.

194
00:09:34,160 --> 00:09:36,389
(The way to Porfi's house
is like a safari tour.)

195
00:09:38,160 --> 00:09:40,230
His house is really far.

196
00:09:40,730 --> 00:09:42,770
- Yungas.
- Yungas?

197
00:09:43,629 --> 00:09:46,869
- This whole area is Yungas.
- Yungas.

198
00:09:46,869 --> 00:09:49,069
- Yungas?
- Yungas.

199
00:09:50,069 --> 00:09:51,980
The area is called Yungas.

200
00:09:52,540 --> 00:09:54,949
There are some houses on the ridges.

201
00:09:55,449 --> 00:09:56,809
Good.

202
00:09:58,050 --> 00:09:59,979
Look on the other side.

203
00:10:01,050 --> 00:10:03,589
There's a waterfall
on the side of the mountain.

204
00:10:03,589 --> 00:10:05,189
- Oh, my.
- It's a waterfall.

205
00:10:05,189 --> 00:10:06,790
The road is very rough.

206
00:10:06,790 --> 00:10:08,490
(They keep going higher,
like they're about to touch the sky.)

207
00:10:08,490 --> 00:10:10,800
How fascinating.

208
00:10:10,800 --> 00:10:13,459
It's fascinating to have come
to a completely different country,

209
00:10:13,459 --> 00:10:15,229
but even within this country,

210
00:10:15,229 --> 00:10:17,839
there's this place you have to drive
seven hours to get to.

211
00:10:18,300 --> 00:10:19,800
(Porfi's house
is very deep inside the mountains.)

212
00:10:19,800 --> 00:10:21,140
Now that I'm here...

213
00:10:22,240 --> 00:10:27,750
Distance wise, it took longer
than going to Eric's house...

214
00:10:27,750 --> 00:10:29,079
in the Amazon.

215
00:10:29,579 --> 00:10:32,920
Let's see
what different cultures they have.

216
00:10:37,089 --> 00:10:38,689
