223
00:10:56,910 --> 00:10:59,839
How long will it take?

224
00:11:00,979 --> 00:11:02,349
Twenty minutes.

225
00:11:02,550 --> 00:11:04,120
Twenty minutes?

226
00:11:04,550 --> 00:11:05,550
(Two fingers)

227
00:11:05,979 --> 00:11:08,250
(Is it 2 or 20 minutes?)

228
00:11:09,949 --> 00:11:11,160
