234
00:11:20,630 --> 00:11:23,329
(Speaking in Spanish)

235
00:11:23,800 --> 00:11:26,069
(What is he saying?)

236
00:11:27,839 --> 00:11:30,569
(He is kindly explaining about this road.)

237
00:11:32,109 --> 00:11:35,179
If I knew this would happen,
I would've brought Pani Bottle.

238
00:11:36,010 --> 00:11:39,179
I wouldn't have left Pani Bottle
with Si Eon.

239
00:11:39,719 --> 00:11:41,819
