250
00:12:01,969 --> 00:12:05,540
Yes. I killed one down there.

251
00:12:06,010 --> 00:12:07,079
Really?

252
00:12:07,780 --> 00:12:10,750
(He is excited by the news
of various wild animals.)

253
00:12:11,679 --> 00:12:13,849
- Do bears attack us?
- Yes.

254
00:12:13,849 --> 00:12:15,420
- They attack us?
- Yes.

255
00:12:16,420 --> 00:12:18,359
My gosh, there are snakes and bears.

256
00:12:18,359 --> 00:12:19,959
(They still manage
to communicate somehow.)

257
00:12:20,790 --> 00:12:22,929
